import React from 'react' import './css/BusLogs.css' function BusLogs ({ buses, dates, sendDate }) { return (
{buses.forEach(bus => (

{buses[0].from.toUpperCase()}

{buses[0].to.toUpperCase()}

{sendDate}

{buses[0].time}

{buses[0].remaining} seats available

{buses[0].totalSeats} total seates.

))}
) } export default BusLogs
